        <title>ACTIVITY: To complete a bar graph [LO 5.4, LO 5.5]</title>
        <para id="id5283288">Bonny and Tommy are 8 years old and their birthday is on 13 May.</para>
        <para id="id5716292">Then they will be ________________________________ years old.</para>
        <list id="id6677059" list-type="bulleted">
          <item>They want to know when your birthdays are. Do you know when your birthday is?</item>
          <item>Now you must help me! (Do you know the names of the months?)</item>
          <item>Put up your hand if I mention the name of the month in which your birthday falls. I will count how many friends have a birthday in each month.</item>
          <item>Write this number in the circle above the name of the month. </item>
