        <list id="id7302431" list-type="bulleted">
          <item>Now we can complete the birthday graph.</item>
        </list>
        <para id="id4770007">Make an X to represent each friend in the month in which his or her birthday falls. </para>
        <para id="id3586629">1. In which month(s) do most of the friends have their birthdays?</para>
        <para id="id8651160">_____________________________________________________________________</para>
        <para id="id4031094">2. In which month(s) do the fewest of the friends have their birthdays?</para>
        <para id="id9399250">_____________________________________________________________________</para>
        <para id="id10675980"/>
        <para id="id7222889">3. What in the graph can change?</para>
        <para id="id9287512">_____________________________________________________________________</para>
        <para id="id4119956"/>
        <para id="id5601538">4. Why can it change?</para>
        <para id="id7755106">_____________________________________________________________________</para>
        <para id="id9779857"/>
        <para id="id4346700">5. What cannot change?</para>
        <para id="id6641787">_____________________________________________________________________</para>
        <para id="id8435179"/>
        <para id="id9302492">Draw a birthday cake with candles on. I want to see how old you are.</para>
